Class InstanceGenerator.NestedArgs

  • java.lang.Object
    • autoweka.InstanceGenerator.NestedArgs
  • Enclosing class:
    InstanceGenerator

    public static class InstanceGenerator.NestedArgs
extends java.lang.Object
    Struct for dealing with nested args on InstanceGenerators that are chained together. Some InstanceGenerators work as a filter on another, this Stuct provides an easy way to split up the arguments to each method
